 back."],[200,275,"She's dead."],[371,600,"And if you don't stop, your wife will be too."],[1184,1280,"What's wrong with you?"],[1280,1334,"You!"],[1480,1618,"You're what's wrong with me?"],[1630,1726,"You filthy!"],[1780,1868,"Con man!"],[1926,2106,"You stole everything from me!"],[2106,2164,"Stop."],[2189,2352,"This is all your fault."],[2448,2519,"Stop!"],[2660,2765,"Oh, look who can talk now."],[2794,2890,"You get a second wind"],[2890,3082,"once I start beating up your boyfriend."],[3082,3261,"He's not my boyfriend."],[3328,3440,"And it's not his fault."],[3440,3520,"It's yours."],[3586,3799,"You chose Amber over your own family."],[3799,3949,"You let our daughter die."],[3991,4079,"You drove me away"],[4079,4170,"when I needed you the most."],[4170,4362,"If you had just listened to me."],[4362,4458,"How could I listen to you?"],[4458,4562,"You just lied."],[4562,4700,"All you do is lie!"],[4725,4879,"Everything you say is a lie"],[4879,5005,"to cover up for your boyfriend."],[5005,5092,"Paul, please."],[5092,5167,"Guards!"],[5246,5351,"Break his arms."],[5384,5501,"Break his legs."],[5572,5714,"And break his fucking jaw."],[5772,5955,"The world needs to know what happens"],[5955,6143,"when you fuck with Paul Hasting!"],[6335,6439,"Get the fuck off me."]],"39":[[25,108,"Paul, please."],[229,346,"Get the fuck off me."],[362,437,"Please, please."],[437,517,"This isn't about him."],[517,663,"This is between you and me."],[842,896,"Okay."],[1084,1234,"Get on your hands and knees"],[1292,1472,"and beg for me to let him go."],[3770,4029,"Please, Paul, I am begging you."],[4066,4233,"Let Xander go."],[4400,4621,"Tell me you're a liar."],[4867,4959,"I’m a liar."],[5121,5217,"Tell me,"],[5334,5476,"you're a bad wife."],[5663,5826,"I'm a bad wife."],[6114,6385,"Tell me you're a horrible mother."],[7052,7278,"Please, I am begging you."]],"40":[[600,746,"I'm a horrible mother."],[1305,1447,"You would say that for him."],[1847,1985,"Now I know you're fucking."],[2039,2106,"